title: The construction of Dutch Navy submarines in 1913 in color! [A.I. enhanced & colorized]

sources.title: The construction of Dutch Navy submarines in 1913 in color! [A.I. enhanced & colorized]
sources.description: An interesting film that shows the construction of Dutch submarines over 110 years ago. The original B&W film has been restored, enhanced and colorized with modern A.I. video software.
